---
import type { jsx } from 'astro/jsx-runtime';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<main>
		<div style='border-radius: 1%; background-color: #ffffff; border: solid black; margin: 10%; margin-top: 5%;' class="mastercard">
		<div class="grid-container">
			<div class="grid-item item1">
				<p class="intro">Hi, I'm Matt</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid-item item2">
				<p>I'm a passionate developer with a focus on web, full stack development and graphic design, I love to tinker and I'm always eager to learn new things and take on new and interesting projects.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid-item item3">
				<img src="https://www.thekennelclub.org.uk/media/3049/caring-for-your-new-puppy.jpg?mode=crop&width=800&height=600&rnd=132137844420000000" alt="">	
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="grid-container">
			<div class="grid-item item4">
				<p>I've been using html and css for a very long time, I also like to use lots of the technologies, I have experience in javascript, flutter, python</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid-item item5">
				<div class="iconcollection">
					<!-- figure out how to read directory -->
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
					<img src="src/media/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png.webp" alt=""> 
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div style="margin: 5%;border-radius: 1%; border: 5px solid green;">
		<div class="centerme">
			<p >This is my most recent project</p>

			<video controls width="50%">
				<source src="src/media/Len.webm" type="video/webm" />
			</video>
			<p>Check out my other projects here...</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Think about a component email form -->
	</div>
		
	</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		

	}

	.centerme {
		display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-direction: column;
		
	}

	.grid-container {
		padding: 2%;

  		

		display: grid;
		gap: 5px;
		
		
	}


	.grid-item {
		
		
	}
	.intro {
		font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
		font-size: 4em;
		margin: 0px;
        
	}
	.item1 {
		text-align: left;
  		grid-column: 1 / span 1;
  		grid-row: 1;

	}

	.item2 {
		display:flex;
		align-items: center;
  		grid-column: 1 ;
  		grid-row: 2;
		
	}


	.item3 {
  		grid-column: 2;
  		grid-row: 1 / span 2;
	}
	.item3 img {
		height: 100%;
		width: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
	}

	.item4 {
		grid-column: 1;
		grid-row: 1;
	}

	.item5 {
		grid-column: 2;
		grid-row: 1;
	}

	.iconcollection {
		margin: 50px;
	}
	.iconcollection img {
		height: 50px;
		
	}

</style>
